{"TopicId":159991,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Moving Inside Spacecrafts","CreatedByName":"KSPFanatic102","CreatedById":153212,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-30T15:34:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"KSPFanatic102","CreatedById":153212,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-30T15:34:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust to ask.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis there any mod that makes kerbals move inside Spacecrafts?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nif not , then\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think Moving inside spacecrafts\u00A0would be cool , and for a additon if i was in kerbin and pressed c then pressed some kind of button i will walk around the spacecraft , if i was in space i would float and \u00A0not walk around .\u00A0i know that the command pods , the Mk1 and Mk2 \u00A0dont have space to move and many others , so i would like to see maybe a movement ability maybe added to the\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/PPD-10_Hitchhiker_Storage_Container\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EPPD-10 Hitchhiker Storage Container\u003C/a\u003E or maybe the\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#252525;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Mobile_Processing_Lab_MPL-LG-2\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMobile Processing Lab MPL-LG-2\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0and possibly\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Mk1_Crew_Cabin\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMk1 Crew Cabin\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0and the \u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Mk3_Passenger_Module\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMk3 Passenger Module\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0,\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/MK2_Crew_Cabin\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMK2 Crew Cabin\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0and to make it simple no more than 1 kerbal can move at a time so the game dosen\u0027t lag and kerbals flying around.\u003C/span\u003E\u00A0and if this is possible , maybe switching seats?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#252525;\u0022\u003E\u00A0other parts that have enough space to move and that could support kerbals.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nI would like to know if it is possible , and what is everyone thoughts .\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSincerely\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTyson Kerman\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTell me below\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-30T16:21:01Z\u0022 title=\u002204/30/2017 04:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 30, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Space_taco\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StupidAndy","CreatedById":171175,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-30T15:56:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntheres a WIP mod that kind of does that\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhere it is!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/159615-12xcoyote-space-industries-cargo-freighter-v017/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nit kind of does that, but not really\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI always thought about moving inside the spacecraft, it would be awesome, and as\u00A0I once said, we can DESIGN THE INTERIOR!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KSPFanatic102","CreatedById":153212,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-30T16:00:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223040069\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493567795\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022171175\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StupidAndy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, StupidAndy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntheres a WIP mod that kind of does that\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhere it is!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/159615-12xcoyote-space-industries-cargo-freighter-v017/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nit kind of does that, but not really\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI always thought about moving inside the spacecraft, it would be awesome, and as\u00A0I once said, we can DESIGN THE INTERIOR!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyeah , but i thought of maybe a Stock one? im fine with a non stock one , but the mod dosen\u0027t Really do it\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ferdoni","CreatedById":140765,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-30T16:16:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhere\u0027s another one that did the job in 1.0 very well. but i think it should indeed be implemented for stock. thats because to give you more \u0027to do\u0027 inside a spacecraft\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/118371-wip-free-iva-formerly-enhanced-iva-alpha-v003-10x-only-2015-10-11/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ngreetz, ferdoni\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-30T16:16:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn stock it\u0027s possible, provided you\u0027re willing to build inside cargo bays and suspend disbelief a little \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0Crews of Kerbfleet capital ships such as KSS \u003Cem\u003EIntrepid \u003C/em\u003Efloat around inside the ship all the time. I \u0022pressurize\u0022 those spaces by editing the config file in the Texture Replacer mod to consider the atmosphere in whatever body\u0027s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E the ship is in to be breathable, with a minimum pressure of 0 kPA. This enables the Kerbs inside to wear their IVA suits, like this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Clwv5rE.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Clwv5rE.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...and as you see Bill demonstrating they can get up, float around, and get to other \u0022pressurized\u0022 spaces in the ship using a\u00A0system of \u0022turbolifts\u0022, i.e. Mk1 lander cans clipped into the bulkheads \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KSPFanatic102","CreatedById":153212,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-30T16:18:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223040087\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493568994\u0022 da